_sText:
de_kaizen is a port of the de_kaizen map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

Executives at Monolith Ventures take over the prefecture of Kaizen. 

MV closes off major areas to traffic during construction causing local business to plummet. 

Eventually outraged businesses leave Kaizen after infinite delays.

MV continues tightening its grip
